a:5:{s:5:"title";s:38:"Salesmate updates quote pricing tables";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:369:"<p>Salesmate refreshed pricing tables with better formatting and typography options to improve readability of packages, add-ons, and totals.</p>
